# =======================================================
# ⚠️ RULE KETAT: JANGAN PERNAH PUSH FOTO, VIDEO, DAN HASIL CLIP
# =======================================================

# 1. Direktori Penampungan Hasil Render & Upload (Berlaku di Semua Microservices)
**/uploads/
**/outputs/
**/temp/
**/tmp/
**/clips/
**/exports/

# 2. Ekstensi File Media Raksasa (Video & Audio)
# Ini mencegah file raw/hasil tercecer di direktori manapun ikut terunggah
*.mp4
*.mkv
*.avi
*.webm
*.mov
*.wav
*.mp3
*.m4a
*.aac
*.flac

# 3. Hasil Generasi AI & Subtitle
*.srt
*.ass
*.vtt

